# Design Token Quick Reference (Tailwind v4)

**All design tokens are defined in `app/globals.css` using the `@theme` directive.**

Use these exact class names when styling components. NEVER use arbitrary values.

## Breakpoints

### Standard Tailwind v4 Breakpoints (RECOMMENDED - Mobile-First)

| Prefix | Min-Width | When to Use |
|--------|-----------|-------------|
| (none) | 0px | Base/mobile styles |
| `sm:` | 640px | Small tablets and up |
| `md:` | 768px | Tablets and up |
| `lg:` | 1024px | Laptops and up |
| `xl:` | 1280px | Desktops and up |
| `2xl:` | 1536px | Large desktops |

**Usage Pattern (Mobile-First):**
```jsx
// Base for mobile, sm: for larger screens
className="px-4 sm:px-10 lg:px-16"
```

### Custom Project Breakpoints (Legacy)

| Prefix | Range | Notes |
|--------|-------|-------|
| `mob:` | max-480px | May not work reliably in v4 |
| `tab:` | 481px-1024px | Use `sm:` or `md:` instead |
| `desk:` | 1025px-1600px | Use `lg:` or `xl:` instead |
| `fw:` | 1601px+ | Use `2xl:` instead |

**IMPORTANT:** Prefer standard Tailwind breakpoints (`sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`) for reliability.

