## VW to Tailwind Conversion

**CRITICAL**: Preserve original layout - converted components must look identical!

Based on [pxvwconverter](https://github.com/RJWadley/pxvwconverter) - different vw values per breakpoint target the **same pixel size**.

### Key Insight
```jsx
// These all produce 200px:
width: 12.5vw;   // At 1600px: 12.5 × 16 = 200px
width: 19.531vw; // At 1024px: 19.531 × 10.24 = 200px  
width: 41.667vw; // At 480px: 41.667 × 4.8 = 200px

// Convert to ONE Tailwind class:
className="w-50" // 12.5rem = 200px
```

### Conversion Formula
```
px = vw × (viewportWidth / 100)
rem = px / 16
```

### Common Conversions

| Target | Desktop (1600px) | Tablet (1024px) | Mobile (480px) | Tailwind |
|--------|------------------|-----------------|----------------|----------|
| 16px | `1vw` | `1.563vw` | `3.333vw` | `4` |
| 40px | `2.5vw` | `3.906vw` | `8.333vw` | `10` |
| 80px | `5vw` | `7.813vw` | `16.667vw` | `20` |
| 100px | `6.25vw` | `9.766vw` | `20.833vw` | `25` |
| 120px | `7.5vw` | `11.719vw` | `25vw` | `30` |
| 148px | `9.25vw` | `14.453vw` | `30.833vw` | `37` |
| 160px | `10vw` | `15.625vw` | `33.333vw` | `40` |
| 200px | `12.5vw` | `19.531vw` | `41.667vw` | `50` |

### PX to Tailwind Class
**Tailwind JIT auto-generates any number**: `number × 0.25rem = size`

**Formula**: `px / 4 = Tailwind number`

| Pixels | Calculation | Tailwind Class |
|--------|-------------|----------------|
| 1304px | 1304 / 4 | `w-326` |
| 1236px | 1236 / 4 | `w-309` |
| 200px | 200 / 4 | `w-50` |
| 100px | 100 / 4 | `w-25` |
| 24px | 24 / 4 | `p-6` |

**DO NOT add custom values to tailwind.config.js** - JIT handles it automatically.

